Background

		Mr. O. Temple Sloan, III, serves as President of General Parts International, Inc. Mr. Sloan served as the President of General Parts International, Inc. from 2001 to 2008. He has been a Trustee of Ravenscroft since 2009. He has been Director of First Bancorp since May 7, 2015. He served as a Director of Advance Auto Parts Inc., from January 2, 2014 to May 18, 2016. He serves as a Trustee of Northwood University. Mr. Sloan served as a Trustee/ Director of General Parts ... International. He served as a director of Car Care Council.Read Full Background




