Temple Sloan: Understanding the man behind the $2 billion deal




Oct 16, 2013, 2:51pm EDT
















Sougata Mukherjee


Editor
Triangle Business Journal









Sougata Mukherjee


 


 







                    Share
                


























 Order Reprints


 Save Article




 Print





 










 



